text.tspan: Output of key industrial sectors in the United Kingdom, 1270 to 1870
This data is indexed to the year 1700, and shows how much industrial output was produced relative to that year.
Data source: Output of key industrial sectors in England - Bank of England (2017)
Note: Data before 1700 refers to England, later data refers to United Kingdom.
